        <div class="page" id="page1">
            <h2>Pattern</h2>
            <p>Syamail, signifying Demeanor or Character, forms the essence of Syamailcoin. This revolutionary cryptocurrency draws inspiration from various mathematical and philosophical works throughout history. These influential ideas, bridging ancient wisdom with modern logic, provide the foundational pattern for Syamailcoin's innovative approach.</p>
            <p>The Syamailcoin logo, the Dagger of Mathematics, pays homage to ancient Roman practices of marking significant documents. This dagger, pointing downwards and encircled by mathematical symbols, bears the number 941 - a key to understanding Syamailcoin's underlying principles.</p>
            <div class="page-number">Page 1</div>
        </div>

        <div class="page" id="page2">
            <h2>Max Supply and Mechanism</h2>
            <p>Syamailcoin's max supply is set at 9,470,000. The system employs a Sleep Time Proof of Elapsed Time of 1.9 seconds, with nodes randomly selected from 0 to 941,000. This mechanism ensures fairness and efficiency in transaction processing.</p>
            <p>The Magic Number 941 is derived from a combination of significant numbers in mathematics and cultural symbolism. It represents a unique value that embodies both mathematical precision and cultural significance, reflecting the holistic approach of Syamailcoin.</p>
            <div class="page-number">Page 2</div>
        </div>

        <div class="page" id="page3">
            <h2>What is Magic Number and why Syamailcoin?</h2>
            <p>The Magic Number 941 is the cornerstone of Syamailcoin's ^S formula. It represents a synthesis of various mathematical and philosophical concepts.</p>
            <p>We can define 941 as a unique number in our system:</p>
            <p>∃x(x = 941 ∧ ∀y(y ≠ x → y ≠ 941)) †</p>
            <p>This logical statement, marked with the Dagger of Maths (†), asserts the unique existence of 941 as our Magic Number.</p>
            <p>Why Syamailcoin? It addresses three critical issues through logical reasoning:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Inflation: Controlled by the ^S formula</li>
                <li>Centralization: Mitigated through distributed node selection</li>
                <li>Market Manipulation: Reduced by transparent, logical mechanisms</li>
            </ol>
            <div class="page-number">Page 3</div>
        </div>

        <div class="page" id="page4">
            <h2>^S is Main Control and Use Cases</h2>
            <p>The ^S formula serves as the main control mechanism for Syamailcoin. Here, ^ symbolizes exponentiation, and S represents the system's state. The Dagger of Maths (†) is used to denote significant mathematical formulas.</p>
            <p>1. Supply Control:</p>
            <p>S(x) = 9,470,000 * (1 - (x / 941)^2) †</p>
            <p>Where x is the current block number. This quadratic decrease ensures a controlled, predictable supply reduction.</p>
            <p>2. Mining Difficulty:</p>
            <p>D(x) = BaseDifficulty * (1 + (x / 941)^3) †</p>
            <p>The cubic increase in difficulty with network growth ensures long-term security and fair distribution.</p>
            <p>These formulas, marked with the Dagger of Maths (†), embody the principle of balancing different aspects of the system to achieve harmony and stability.</p>
